title: Drill Here Now
description: Fellas discuss Democrats' refusal to tap American energy resources and laugh about Hillary's comeback before playing a game of Veep or VP. Arizona Attorney General Mark Brnovich joins the progrum for an interview about his race for U.S. Senate.
author: hello@ruthlesspodcast.com (John Ashbrook, Josh Holmes, Michael Duncan, Comfortably Smug, Mark Brnovich)
